name: Warped Space Shooter
description:
This is a Game Template for a Space Shooter made in Godot.

You can use it to learn or create your own game from it. Do whatever you want with the code and the Assets. 

Artwork included:

  • Player Sprites
  • Enemy Sprites
  • Asteroids Sprites
  • Music Track
  • Sound Effects
  • Seamless Looped Backgrounds

Code, Artwork, Sounds and Music by Ansimuz
